{"id":533081,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/01/【立此存照】-军事新闻和信息/","date":"2015-01-22T20:09:49Z","modified":"2017-02-06T19:31:11Z","title":"【立此存照】军事新闻和信息","content":"<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-533082\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/CliJRJXUYAABXAA.jpg\" alt=\"CliJRJXUYAABXAA\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/CliJRJXUYAABXAA.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/CliJRJXUYAABXAA-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/CliJRJXUYAABXAA-768x577.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/CliJRJXUYAABXAA-1024x769.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>一，军事新闻和信息要由经过授权的机构和人员发布；</p>\n<p>二，对反军乱军言论要坚决取缔，并依法制裁；</p>\n<p>三，对重大网络泄密事件要追究责任，依法处理。</p>\n<p>四，对重大事件要有表态口径，界定哪些话可以说，哪些话不可以说，说到什么程度。可以设计红白脸，甚至战略误导。</p>\n","author":999,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,31660,27949],"tags":[8635,23882,12116]}